      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah, exactly. like, if it’s all just going to be erased anyway, why even put in the effort? the \"shining moment\" thing sounds nice in a poem, but in reality it just feels like a waste of energy. we're just suffering through this tiny bit of time for nothing. if the end result is always zero, doesn't that make the struggle itself seem pretty irrational?",
